title: Britain’s Got Talent coming to Falsgrave CRC (Scarborough Borough Council)
text: ( Source : Scarborough Borough Council ) Aspiring entertainers of all ages are being invited to audition their skills on Sunday 25 October when the production team from the hugely popular ITV show, Britain's Got Talent , rolls into Scarborough.
